com.bmd.android.collection.filter

Interface SparseArrayCompatFilterBuilder<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the entry value type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    FilterBuilder<SparseArrayCompatIterable<V>,SparseArrayEntry<V>>

    public interface SparseArrayCompatFilterBuilder<V>
extends FilterBuilder<SparseArrayCompatIterable<V>,SparseArrayEntry<V>>
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling SparseArrayEntry elements.
